{"tid":769857,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「冷撥打」 強積金騙局 預設投資策略","createTime":"2018-08-06T13:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T11:35:38.000Z","uid":116505,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c009ea23e2ef7547b731a1cabe78fefb8d1c716a","tid":769857,"uid":116505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"今日返緊工收到個強姦局打電話黎 事後諗返起係一個保險狗圈套<br />\n<br />\n一打黎話因爲強姦金改左玩法 全港由4月1號改左做預設投資策略 打黎既目的係教我係新制度下點揀強積金 <br />\n<br />\n佢提到聽日全日幫全港市民手分析強積金 聲稱<br />\n1）呢個策略會令打工仔無得控制基金組合 無得掌握賺蝕<br />\n2）星斗市民好難轉投資策略<br />\n3）想約我出黎 同時約緊全港市民講解 （我hi 做咩吹到咁大）<br />\n我叫佢比啲証明 佢話到時見面再提供 可以睇完佢地公司証件再聽佢地分析同佢地所謂既&rdquo;轉策略&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我因為一路做緊其他野分左心 答應左佢聽日下就見面 聽日我得閒可以單挑下佢地 但未諗好點玩🤔<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊間垃圾公司既新傳銷策略 真係好狗 係到扮政府代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9c904f0d7ea6b536a7594f202d33b38cfc7f89","tid":769857,"uid":10687,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:51:55.000Z","msg":"自己想見就見啦，做野分心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67166aef09b090d8bf88720b79b084462be58bef","tid":769857,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c009ea23e2ef7547b731a1cabe78fefb8d1c716a","tid":769857,"uid":116505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"今日返緊工收到個強姦局打電話黎 事後諗返起係一個保險狗圈套<br />\n<br />\n一打黎話因爲強姦金改左玩法 全港由4月1號改左做預設投資策略 打黎既目的係教我係新制度下點揀強積金 <br />\n<br />\n佢提到聽日全日幫全港市民手分析強積金 聲稱<br />\n1）呢個策略會令打工仔無得控制基金組合 無得掌握賺蝕<br />\n2）星斗市民好難轉投資策略<br />\n3）想約我出黎 同時約緊全港市民講解 （我hi 做咩吹到咁大）<br />\n我叫佢比啲証明 佢話到時見面再提供 可以睇完佢地公司証件再聽佢地分析同佢地所謂既&rdquo;轉策略&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我因為一路做緊其他野分左心 答應左佢聽日下就見面 聽日我得閒可以單挑下佢地 但未諗好點玩🤔<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊間垃圾公司既新傳銷策略 真係好狗 係到扮政府代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"陪佢玩 約出黎 錄音拍片 地點你定 最好揾多幾個朋友 坐附近扮唔識 有事都可以求救"},{"pid":"3356b402742b430940a690a66e3f575ae5f825df","tid":769857,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"可能係fwd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d8986f02ae1b820c57265a48cbc51ea1c3c82e","tid":769857,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"佢會幫你買forward黎hedge <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154771f7e1f4d9b1eaf5aa5cec9ee86ebecbb9dd","tid":769857,"uid":123812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:03:35.000Z","msg":"9成9係保險佬或者d IFA"},{"pid":"6d7bbd1303f48dfbd1c52bcc4f95aadbbdfefc50","tid":769857,"uid":116505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/YcW3fYM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FYcW3fYM&h=7f476b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\njunk call database 顯示係傳銷黎 聽日佢打黎決定抄牌再report上強姦局"},{"pid":"7424e9880176878dcd56cdc862b79d60c44b6818","tid":769857,"uid":116505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/231239_75639d4112bb5a157b65bb18136ccd4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F231239_75639d4112bb5a157b65bb18136ccd4e.jpg&h=3e69be53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ceb8694172f7d61f8c96dfd98d2c8fd006edb994","tid":769857,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"佢有無推介邊隻基金俾你 佢無證卷牌可以錄音告佢"},{"pid":"cdeab1b802c48b354b4f41c0cdd05b5ebb1ffb10","tid":769857,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"上年有有自稱老強人員打左比我幾次<br />\n話要配合政府講下新老強安排<br />\n我約左佢3次 放左佢飛機3次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後聽講佢地係將cold call賣比sales 每個好似百幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主不妨約佢地之後放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476917040ce5e11e326ce120a4a6b445e83a5077","tid":769857,"uid":116505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:12:17.000Z","msg":"想佢地錄音 放飛機 再報驚"},{"pid":"0dd6977bf16d85d96d6c434d4ebeaf63320c153e","tid":769857,"uid":70684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:34:03.000Z","msg":"其實成個預設投資策略 (DIS) 只不過係基金公司開多2隻基金出黎<br />\n<br />\n2隻基金分別係 Core Accumulation Fund (CAF) 同 Age 65 Plus Fund (A65F)<br />\nCAF當中有55%-65%係買high risk asset, A65F就係25%-35%係買low risk asset, 呢個allocation係受到MPFA既監管的<br />\n<br />\n咁成個DIS最主要既原素係佢有de-risking既成份<br />\n當你由51歲開始至60歲,每年你既生日, 佢都會幫你轉特定investment percentage由CAF去A65F, 咁就做到derisking既成份<br />\n<br />\n除此之外, 就係收費<br />\n由於DIS係MPFA推既野, 所以收費都會受到MPFA監管, 當中包括基金日常支出會係控制係不多於基金價值(NAV)既0.75%, 而其他支出就係不多於NAV 0.2%. 如果多過既話, 基金公司係要主動向MPFA申報<br />\n<br />\n當中樓主提及如果轉其他基金會受到限制, 其實唔會的, 你就算揀左DIS, 你任何時候都可以轉走的"},{"pid":"0838872d6467f9aaabfef83bea2ea627ea328914","tid":769857,"uid":70684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實成個預設投資策略 (DIS) 只不過係基金公司開多2隻基金出黎<br />\n<br />\n2隻基金分別係 Core Accumulation Fund (CAF) 同 Age 65 Plus Fund (A65F)<br />\nCAF當中有55%-65%係買high risk asset, A65F就係25%-35%係買low risk asset, 呢個allocation係受到MPFA既監管的<br />\n<br />\n咁成個DIS最主要既原素係佢有de-risking既成份<br />\n當你由51歲開始至<span style=\"color: red;\">65</span>歲,每年你既生日, 佢都會幫你轉特定investment percentage由CAF去A65F, 咁就做到derisking既成份<br />\n<br />\n除此之外, 就係收費<br />\n由於DIS係MPFA推既野, 所以收費都會受到MPFA監管, 當中包括基金日常支出會係控制係不多於基金價值(NAV)既0.75%, 而其他支出就係不多於NAV 0.2%. 如果多過既話, 基金公司係要主動向MPFA申報<br />\n<br />\n當中樓主提及如果轉其他基金會受到限制, 其實唔會的, 你就算揀左DIS, 你任何時候都可以轉走的</blockquote>"},{"pid":"083d1b59f8477b01fbd19b233ad409361ba44da2","tid":769857,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:58:16.000Z","msg":"之前又係有間扮強績金<br />\n點知講講下變倫敦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心唸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e75e411c286bbd4c979729a87c1d3b6f9b7f3a","tid":769857,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"放過佢哋飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f929e98203dd53e4bf02dfe4576fadd564e53343","tid":769857,"uid":116505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:44:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱有條姓黃既打嚟 夠膽話自己係康宏 屌到佢飛天 琴日話自己強積金管理局 係到扮政府 話咩到定要你地幫手 正臭雞 <br />\n<br />\n佢叫我冷靜 我同佢講你成間機構呃緊人 點冷靜 屌多兩句就收左佢線 點解呢個香港咁多傳銷狗"},{"pid":"ffeeec532ac6a8260cddfadb0e1495430ae9dd9f","tid":769857,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f929e98203dd53e4bf02dfe4576fadd564e53343","tid":769857,"uid":116505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:44:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱有條姓黃既打嚟 夠膽話自己係康宏 屌到佢飛天 琴日話自己強積金管理局 係到扮政府 話咩到定要你地幫手 正臭雞 <br />\n<br />\n佢叫我冷靜 我同佢講你成間機構呃緊人 點冷靜 屌多兩句就收左佢線 點解呢個香港咁多傳銷狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:47:27.000Z","msg":"我都收到，條友講到一舊舊，最後被我chok到佢係代表康宏持牌顧問打嚟，想約時間和我見面，究竟咩事？"},{"pid":"3a0392f4c6346c50c18578144cf9ed9d11deab44","tid":769857,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffeeec532ac6a8260cddfadb0e1495430ae9dd9f","tid":769857,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f929e98203dd53e4bf02dfe4576fadd564e53343","tid":769857,"uid":116505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:44:12.000Z","